name: Eat Me Arisu
description:
Meet Arisu, she would eat anything with or without an "eat me" label on it. A little bit of gluttony issues here.

Consiisting of: Sourdough, Raspberry & Vanilla Buttercream Spongecake, Cube Croissant topped with Chocolate Sauce, Strawberry Shortcake, Rasberry Compote Brownies inside a Red Velvet Spongecake covered in Glaze, and a Butter Croissant.
